Simplicity IT Sentinel to Defender XDR Migration Toolkit
=========================================================

This toolkit incorporates code from the Microsoft Azure-Sentinel
community repository, specifically Mario Cuomo's Defender Adoption
Helper script:

    https://github.com/mariocuomo/Azure-Sentinel/tree/master/Tools/Sentinel-Defender-Helper-Script/New%20Version

