Original author of the bundled script: Mario Cuomo, Microsoft Security.

Files retained verbatim from the upstream project, with original
copyright headers preserved:

  src/DefenderAdoptionHelper.ps1
  config/sentinelEnvironments.json
  output/dashboard.html

Files net-new under this fork, copyright Simplicity IT Inc., 2026,
licensed under the same MIT terms as the upstream:

  src/SimplicityWorkbooksInventory.ps1     (planned)
  src/SimplicityPlaybookInventory.ps1      (planned)
  src/SimplicityHuntingQueryInventory.ps1  (planned)
  src/SimplicityWatchlistInventory.ps1     (planned)
  src/SimplicityConnectorMap.ps1           (planned)
  src/Run-FullAssessment.ps1               (planned)
